{"tid":2360701,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【培養良好習慣】過萬條Trump嘅tweet一夜消失：以後link嘢可唔可以習慣整個archive link？","createTime":"2021-01-10T04:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T10:54:02.000Z","uid":131691,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f075392131da5865ae9d71e4dbc44ea909b1038c","tid":2360701,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"今次Trump個Twitter account就咁就消失咗，基本上所有之前link出嚟嘅tweet係一夜間消失哂。<br />\n唔係淨係連登，基本上全世界嘅傳媒如果呢4年引述Trump都係就咁擺條tweet link就算，基本上係個quote完全消失咗。<br />\n大家可唔可以培養返一個貼link要archive嘅習慣？<br />\n<br />\n呢讓嘢唔係淨係引用Trump先要做，係link嘢時候嘅良好習慣嚟。<br />\n不論你係左定右，親美定親中定親歐定親港，都係好事嚟，因爲你永遠唔知你quote緊嘅媒體（可能係社交媒體Twitter/Facebook/Instagram/Gab/etc.，亦都可能係傳統媒體BBC/New York Times/People's Daily/etc.）幾時會突然間bam account/嗰個人自己set做private/網站轉format啲舊link死哂/嗰個人自己del po/媒體事後改內容/etc.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">Archive一頁其實好易，直接將個網址擺入 <a href=\"https://archive.today/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.today%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c072819e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.today/</a> 就得。</span></strong><br />\n唔好依賴Wayback Machine（即係 <a href=\"http://archive.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.org&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c2aa3331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">archive.org</a>）嘅自動時光機archive，<a href=\"http://因爲唔少網站係set咗唔想archive.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9B%A0%E7%88%B2%E5%94%94%E5%B0%91%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E4%BF%82set%E5%92%97%E5%94%94%E6%83%B3archive.org&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=f929c2c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">因爲唔少網站係set咗唔想archive.org</a>自動archive。你手動擺入去 <a href=\"https://archive.today/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.today%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c072819e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.today/</a> 基本上係永世keep。"},{"pid":"bca03ec215e0af4fb32438fd08fdd0e63f84b498","tid":2360701,"uid":86509,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n自從魏巴自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚高學歷巴自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打們要小心啲acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c7e87ae0420de27cbe18f7733beff18339840d","tid":2360701,"uid":195904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"你條link死埋咁點？"},{"pid":"140378bb6f2e81f42a542e56c9d181fd599372a9","tid":2360701,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"都就黎落台啦，仲搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9d0bd0a356d7e1de2a5f5697f705fcbeffa4dd","tid":2360701,"uid":60334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"你個網死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e33c7bb8e56c41a38de87809f58a47678291641","tid":2360701,"uid":54721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"成段歷史都冇晒<br />\n之後就任佢地寫"},{"pid":"b81a5e5912cc33e14f1702d00f87b30c0b861c8f","tid":2360701,"uid":189961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"連Parler個server都比人禁埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41d1ff78c515cb3344c217859b65ab9a30f8875","tid":2360701,"uid":131691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"archive.today 係用嚟archive一頁嘅網站，如果係一條片嘅話，最好係自己用 youtube-dl （唔係淨係for youtube，幾乎咩網頁都work）download成條片落嚟。<br />\n<br />\n坊間有人會直接用 streamable 呢啲網站，但係佢係三個月後就會delete，所以我真係建議學吓用youtube-dl算<br />\n<br />\n唔